;           (supervisor ?x ?middle-manager)))
;
;查询 (wheel ?x ?middle-manager ?who) 结果为
;
;(wheel (Cratchet Robert) (Scrooge Eben) (Warbucks Oliver))
;(wheel (Tweakit Lem E) (Bitdiddle Ben) (Warbucks Oliver))
